FBIS3-51081 "drlat009_l_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-009 Document Type:Daily Report 13 Jan 1994 Bolivia Human Rights Leader Criticizes U.S. Embassy `Onslaught' PY1201131194 La Paz Radio Fides Network in Spanish 1100 GMT 12 Jan 94 PY1201131194 La Paz Radio Fides Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Report by Edwin Mallon Avalos, the Radio Fides correspondent in Cochabamba] [Text] During a news conference, the Permanent Assembly for Human Rights [APDH], along with various groups such as peasant organizations and the Departmental Workers Federation, reported a U.S. Embassy onslaught against those who dare to report DEA abuses in our national territory. This remark was made by Dr. Victor Gutierrez, the APDH president in Cochabamba.
